metadata.name: Azure Gaze
metadata.description: Azure Gaze is a surreal and hauntingly beautiful figure. Her face dominates the composition, with large blue eyes that seem to peer into the depths of your soul. Her features merge seamlessly with the surrounding structures, as if she is one with the very fabric of the environment. Despite her otherworldly appearance, there is a sense of melancholy and longing in her expression, as if she is searching for something just out of reach. Azure Gaze is a stunning embodiment of the beauty and mystery of the surreal world.
